text: Solnhofen is a municipality in Weißenburg-Gunzenhausen in Middle Franconia in the of Bavaria in Germany. It is in the Altmühl valley. ==Geography== Solnhofen is on the Altmühl in Bavaria. It has two districts: Hochholz and Eßlingen. It is next to the cities Pappenheim, Langenaltheim and Mörnsheim. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Solnhofen fossils * Bürgermeister Müller Museum Category:Weißenburg-Gunzenhausen
